description:
What is the process of an inspirational book being written? How does an idea, counsel, or teaching, go from a vision to the printed page? This episode outlines the meticulous process that would occur whenever a book for the Seventh Day Adventist Church was written.

To find out more about Ellen White's books visit our website to read our extended article.
